' offhand weapon slots in slots 7 n' 8 on da hotkey bar.  Den I puts da bottom 2 inventory slots on da 9 n' 10 hotkey slots...  Much gud!  Yoo can swap dem out easilly, jes by clickin on da weapon n' droppin it into yer weapon slot on da hotkey box. <p><center><img src=http://extremeannihilation.nimueserver.com/images/cj_sig.gif border=0><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=221997" target="_blank"><font size="2">Ma Stuff</a> - <a href="http://harbingers.cjb.net" target="_blank">Ma Guild</a> - <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior" target="_blank">Ma Hangout</a></font></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujuleena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Juleena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/12/02 9:54:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> Translation...?= put inventory into macro slot? Something like...what? /inventory 4 or whatever? Woodelves lil slow till we get goin...hehe. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usharak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 139<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/12/02 10:02:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ldguild.net/ldnews/images/dollz/sharakaidollz.gif HEIGHT=160 WIDTH=140></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> Open up your inventory.  Hover your mouse over one of your inventory slots (melee 1, melee 2, or any of the inventory slots).  Hold down your mouse button.  Eventually, that inventory slot will appear as a button on your cursor (you can release the mouse key).  Go down to your hot button bar and place it where you want it to show up.<br><br>Do the same for another inventory slot (or melee slot).<br><br>Now, when you want to swap weapons, you have those slots easily available in your hotkey setup (they act like your regular inventory screen).  Just left click to pick up a weapon out of your hotkey setup and place it in your other inventory/melee slot on the hot button bar.<br><br>Be careful with droppable/tradable weapons! <p>Sharak'Duom 51 Ghost<br>Keroppi'Duom 60 Godzilla<br>Sharakai'Duom 59 Ronin<br><center><a href="http://www.ldguild.net"><img src="http://www.ldguild.net/ldnews/images/dollz/ldbanner.gif" alt="Lumiere Divine, Zebuxoruk" border="0"></A></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usharak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharak</A> at: 7/12/02 10:03:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujuleena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Juleena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/12/02 11:01:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> TANKIES!!!! =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ucomparisonjones.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Comparison Jones</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>YARG! No pokin da fat rolls!</span><br>  Posts: 629<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/12/02 3:10:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.nimueserver.com/images/personal/comp_head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> Wut, yoo nos understood me?  Bah, yoo needs ter learn Ogie-ish, den yoo woulds understands me fine har har! <p><center><img src=http://extremeannihilation.nimueserver.com/images/cj_sig.gif border=0><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=221997" target="_blank"><font size="2">Ma Stuff</a> - <a href="http://harbingers.cjb.net" target="_blank">Ma Guild</a> - <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior" target="_blank">Ma Hangout</a></font></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubesrikarle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Besrikarle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/13/02 4:26:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> Here is my setup. It has the melee slots, the ability to taunt and kick while changing if needed, two bags linking to weapons, and 4 slots of right click items I use frequently.<br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/besrikarle/weaponswap1.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Now I push '6' to open my primary weapons bag. Number 5 are more utility like.<br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/besrikarle/weaponswap2.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Now I am switching from a dual weild setup to a 2hander. I left click my secondary item to get it onto cursor.<br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/besrikarle/weaponswap3.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Now place the secondart slot item over the 2hander, and left click to replace it. Then drag the 2hander to the primary slot.<br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/besrikarle/weaponswap4.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Finally, left click the Axe to swap the 1h primary with the 2hander. Deposit the 1hander back into the bag in its rightful place and close the bag.<br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/besrikarle/weaponswap5.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>This whole process takes about one second or less. By choosing which weapon to pick up first and replace, you can cutdown the time of switching and cutdown on potential unarmed attacks. With tradeable no-drop items, I have mine set to a confirmation box. The box disapears when the item is placed back into the bag. Either use the box or just turn off dropping and trading or whatnot.<br><br>Hope this helps you out some. <p><BR>Besrikarle Armiger`Yasdnil<BR>Halfling Warlord<BR>Five Rings<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/umintzyfresch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mintzy Fresch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 476<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/13/02 9:43:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/uryvichk/minpro2.jpg width=100 height=145></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> You can do similar for ghetto-bashing with a shield. Just have your secondary slot adjacent to an inventory slot containing a shield, click when you start combat to float the shield, then click after your secondary swings, hit bash, click again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uheugel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heugel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/17/02 10:52:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> whoops... Screenshot didn't work...  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uheugel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heugel</A> at: 7/17/02 10:53:03 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uzytalius71.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zytalius71</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/17/02 11:30:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hotkey Setup</span><hr size=1> Would go even faster if they allowed Bag Slot to be Hotkeyed.  Saves one extra step from opening a bag up.  <br><br>But remember to put your bag at the bottom of the inventory slot that has your weapons to be switch.  If you are a looting horde, then those bag slots get filled up pretty fast.  nothing is worse than wanted to do a fast weapon change and realize the bag now has junk items in the slots.  Now you have to go searching for some room in other bags.  Soo annoying.<br><br><br> <p>Zytalius     < 60th Warlord - Drinal ><BR><BR>-= For Victory, Believe in Steel and the Warriors that wield them =-</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showNextMessage?topicID=955.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=955.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.emailToFriend?topicID=955.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.threadControl?topicID=955.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=955.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=955.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteelwarriorthebunker">The Bunker<option value="thesteelwarriorthetavern">The Tavern<option value="thesteelwarriorfrm6">The Keep</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table></form></td></tr></